   <p>Lighthouse Villas is a town house complex in the ocean side section of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/corolla/corolla-light.asp" title="Corolla Light">Corolla Light</a>. There are 68 units, all of them have 4 bedrooms and 3.5 baths. The complex is located just a short walk from the ocean front pool and activity center with easy ocean access. Shopping and dining is another short walk away so the Lighthouse Villas are one of the few places where you can park your car and never use it during your entire vacation. </p>
